{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSockets","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/WebSockets","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>WebSocket 是一种在客户端与<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Server\">服务器</a>之间保持<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/TCP\">TCP</a>长连接的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">网络协议</a>，这样它们就可以随时进行信息交换。</p>\n<p>虽然任何客户端或服务器上的应用都可以使用 WebSocket，但原则上还是指<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Browser\">浏览器</a>与服务器之间使用。通过 WebSocket，服务器可以直接向客户端发送数据，而无须客户端周期性的请求服务器，以动态更新数据内容。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入了解","title":"深入了解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知识","title":"基本知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Websocket\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Websocket</a> 维基百科</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\">WebSocket 的 MDN 参考</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习了解","title":"学习了解","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\">编写 WebSocket 客户端应用</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_servers\">编写 WebSocket 服务器应用</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入了解","id":"深入了解"}],"summary":"WebSocket 是一种在客户端与服务器之间保持TCP长连接的网络协议，这样它们就可以随时进行信息交换。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WebSockets","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"We